<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Preparing a sample document</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  For this walkthrough, you can use any text document (.txt, .docx, .html). We recommend
  using a real council document - perhaps a council tax notice, tenancy agreement, or planning
  notification. The more realistic the content, the more meaningful the translation.
</p>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
    <strong>Tip:</strong> If you don't have a document handy, create a simple text file with
    a few sentences of English text. The tool works with any plain text.
  </p>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Uploading and translating</h3>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Navigate to Document Translation</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      From the sidebar, click <strong>Document Translation</strong> then <strong>Create Translation Job</strong>.
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Upload your document</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Click the upload area or drag your file into it. The source language will be detected automatically.
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Select target languages</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Choose at least two languages - we suggest <strong>Welsh (cy)</strong> and <strong>Polish (pl)</strong>.
      Welsh is important for councils in Wales with legal bilingual obligations. Polish is one of the most
      spoken community languages in UK councils.
    </p>
  </li>

<div class="ndx-walkthrough-step__screenshot govuk-!-margin-top-4 govuk-!-margin-bottom-4">
  <img src="/assets/images/screenshots/simply-readable/03-upload-interface.png"
       alt="Document upload interface showing a sample council tax notice with Welsh and Polish selected as target languages"
       class="ndx-walkthrough-step__image"
       loading="lazy">
  <p class="ndx-walkthrough-step__screenshot-caption govuk-body-s">Upload a document and select target languages - here translating a council tax notice to Welsh and Polish</p>
</div>

  <li>
    <strong>Submit the translation</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Click <strong>Translate</strong>. For short documents, translation completes in seconds.
      Larger documents may take a minute or two.
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Download translated files</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Once complete, download each translated file. Open them to verify the translation quality.
    </p>
  </li>
</ol>

<div class="ndx-walkthrough-step__screenshot govuk-!-margin-top-4 govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
  <img src="/assets/images/screenshots/simply-readable/04-translation-completed.png"
       alt="Translation progress view showing Welsh and Polish translations completed with download links"
       class="ndx-walkthrough-step__image"
       loading="lazy">
  <p class="ndx-walkthrough-step__screenshot-caption govuk-body-s">Both translations complete in seconds - ready to download</p>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Understanding the cost savings</h3>

<div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-!-margin-top-4">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <div class="ndx-comparison-card ndx-comparison-card--before">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Traditional translation</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~£160 per document</p>
      <p class="govuk-body"><strong>Time:</strong> Up to 19 days</p>
      <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-0"><strong>Swindon's annual spend:</strong> £64,000 (Paediatric Therapy alone)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <div class="ndx-comparison-card ndx-comparison-card--after">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Amazon Translate</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~£0.07 per document</p>
      <p class="govuk-body"><strong>Time:</strong> Under 14 minutes</p>
      <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-0"><strong>Swindon's new annual spend:</strong> £27</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-4">
  That's a <strong>99.96% cost reduction</strong> and a <strong>6,300,000% ROI</strong> based on
  Swindon Borough Council's published figures.
</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Quick Text translation</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  You can also try <strong>Quick Text</strong> from the sidebar for instant text translation
  without uploading a file. Type or paste text, select a target language, and see the
  translation appear immediately.
</p>

<details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-top-6">
  <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
    <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
      Troubleshooting: Translation not completing
    </span>
  </summary>
  <div class="govuk-details__text">
    <p class="govuk-body">If translation doesn't complete:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>Check the file format is supported (.txt, .docx, .html, .xlf, .xlsx, .pptx)</li>
      <li>Large documents take longer - wait up to 5 minutes</li>
      <li>Try the Quick Text feature to verify translation is working</li>
      <li>Check the browser console for any error messages</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</details>

